doc_summary_long: FARMINGTON HILLS (WWJ) - Police were called to deal with a disturbance Wednesday, at an Oakland County Sam's Club that is slated to close. One of two Michigan Sam's Club stores set to close, the Farmington Hills location will be shuttered for good on Saturday. Parent company Wal-Mart Inc. announced last week that it would close dozens of Sam's Club stores nationwide.
doc_summary_short: FARMINGTON HILLS (WWJ) - Police were called to deal with a disturbance Wednesday, at an Oakland County Sam's Club that is slated to close.
doc_title: 'Absolutely Insane Scene': Police Deal With Unruly Crowd At Farmington Hills Sam's Club
